Silksprite
==========

Rails helper for Silksprite
http://www.ajaxbestiary.com/Labs/SilkSprite/

How to use
==========
include stylesheets in your layout file:
  <%= silksprite_stylesheets %>

To place a icon on your page:
  <%= silksprite symbol %>
where symbol is the name of the sprite.


Example
=======
 silksprite(:tick)
 # => <span class="ss_sprite ss_tick">&nbsp;</span>
 

